WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:04.758
Hey, good morning family, praise the Lord, or good afternoon, wherever you are.

00:00:04.759 --> 00:00:15.359
Hello, welcome, thank you for joining us. It's 2025. We're right now at New Year's Eve doing this video.

00:00:15.360 --> 00:00:20.018
I've been interceding for this New Year all the last several days.

00:00:20.019 --> 00:00:32.300
We've had such intense intercession going on in our house, praying for the nations and asking what the Lord has in store for 2025.

00:00:32.301 --> 00:00:43.048
This is a very serious time. The Lord told me there would be two different words: one for the ones that are awake and one for the ones that are lukewarm.

00:00:43.049 --> 00:00:49.497
You will see the ones that are awake and on fire for Him, who have their lamps full of oil.

00:00:49.498 --> 00:00:58.277
We talked about this remnant of people who will see great change as the harvesters.

00:00:58.278 --> 00:01:05.461
You will see a mighty anointing and a transfer of wealth from the sinner laid up for the righteous.

00:01:05.462 --> 00:01:10.514
If you are staying vertical with Him, you will hear in this window.

00:01:10.515 --> 00:01:40.332
The Lord said, 'I'm giving you a window, remnant; I'm giving you a window for a great acceleration of prosperity and preparation, like the Josephs, for what is coming.'How big the window is, I don't know, but he said in this window, if you're listening to Him and staying vertical, you will hear Him on what you're supposed to be doing.

00:01:40.333 --> 00:01:52.022
To the ones that are lukewarm, this will be a time of great shaking to awaken you.

00:01:52.023 --> 00:02:02.807
He said, 'Brandon, I will take care of My beloved.'He talked to us about it in an hour-long word.

00:02:02.808 --> 00:02:12.238
He said, 'You are My beloved and I bring gifts.'Thank you, Holy Spirit.

00:02:12.239 --> 00:02:51.299
He said, 'I bring gifts to the bride before the Bridegroom comes for the wedding.'He said, 'I am standing at the door listening for My Father's instruction for Him to tell Me to come back for My bride.'In Jewish tradition, the groom always gives gifts to the bride before the wedding.

00:02:51.300 --> 00:03:05.859
He said He was bringing forth great giftings and romance to the bride.

00:03:05.860 --> 00:03:29.512
He said, 'Brandon, I am the God of the cattle on a thousand hills, for My gifts are great and vast; I have streets of gold.'He told me the wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous, but it is about a kingly Him; He's the King of kings and the Lord of lords.

00:03:29.513 --> 00:03:57.758
As the Bridegroom is wooing the bride and getting ready for the marriage feast, for the marriage supper of the Lamb, there is a major exchange of romance toward His church.

00:03:57.759 --> 00:04:23.594
I saw an impartation of angelic visitations and manifestations of glory—healings and things your mind cannot comprehend.

00:04:23.595 --> 00:04:40.594
The King is coming, and it is a time of celebration for the bride and the groom.

00:04:40.595 --> 00:04:47.621
He was telling me all this stuff is going to start taking place with a great acceleration of change.

00:04:47.622 --> 00:04:59.098
2025 will be a year of great change. Then I heard, 'War, war, war.'It will be talked about on the news.

00:04:59.099 --> 00:05:16.570
2025 will be known for war. I saw conflict between America and China at the Panama Canal.

00:05:16.571 --> 00:05:58.879
I saw a red dragon flapping its wings, and I heard the Spirit of the Lord say, 'The Panama Canal, for there is great corruption, but as Donald Trump cracks his whip, he will tame the dragon.'I saw Donald Trump standing there like a circus ringmaster with a black coat with long tails and a white shirt with a black bow tie.

00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:35.672
He was cracking a whip to tame the dragon. I saw the dragon snapping and gnashing its teeth at him, but it was flying backwards as he cracked his whip.

00:06:35.673 --> 00:06:57.785
The dragon was being tamed and retreating. A communistic spirit has tried to come over America as an extension from this dragon, but you will see that agenda broken.

00:06:57.786 --> 00:07:36.888
I saw Kim Jong-un and China; they were flapping their wings, and he was taming Kim Jong-un and the Chinese party.

00:07:36.889 --> 00:08:05.719
This is a demonic principality that has tried to influence our government through the Democratic party through hidden doors.

00:08:05.720 --> 00:08:37.474
These things of communism will be broken. I saw Justin Trudeau being removed from his position.

00:08:37.475 --> 00:09:01.994
The Lord said there would be a dividing line between the far left and the far right, and you will see a Holy Ghost revival from sea to sea.

00:09:01.995 --> 00:09:09.702
He said even Justin Trudeau and Emmanuel Macron will be dealt with.

00:09:09.703 --> 00:09:34.045
He said because of Macron holding back, he's trying to bring a New World Order over Europe.

00:09:34.046 --> 00:09:57.751
The people of Canada have cried out, and I will deliver thee; there will be revival that breaks forth from shore to shore, and you will soar.

00:09:57.752 --> 00:10:27.342
Justin Trudeau's days are numbered. There will be a dividing between the far left and the right, and it will happen overnight.

00:10:27.343 --> 00:10:34.388
He told me He was going to deal with Emmanuel Macron also, but he showed me that there would be great revival in Europe.

00:10:34.389 --> 00:10:48.510
He said, 'You try to stop My gospel, I will deal with you also,'and He spoke of the Antichrist spirit.

00:10:48.511 --> 00:11:10.078
There will be revival in France and Europe. Donald Trump will be putting these people in check, dealing with Putin, the bear.

00:11:10.079 --> 00:11:16.833
I saw him cracking his whip across the nations, and it was bringing change.

00:11:16.834 --> 00:11:47.625
A whip only tames the animal; it doesn't destroy it. It causes the animal to pause.

00:11:47.626 --> 00:11:58.680
It's about His presence allowing for one last call and bringing freedom for His people to hear.

00:11:58.681 --> 00:12:28.212
It is a window for the last push to bring in the harvest. You will see the animal bow down for a little bit, giving a window of time to move.

00:12:28.213 --> 00:13:00.819
The bear sat down and paused, but it was still ready to roar. It gave a window for revival in Russia and for things to happen with China.

00:13:00.820 --> 00:13:45.096
I saw the rising sun over Taiwan and the remnant church interceding. I saw it glowing with glory and a revival taking place.

00:13:45.097 --> 00:13:50.028
He needs you to help pray; that's why I called you to this channel to pray for Donald Trump.

00:13:50.029 --> 00:14:04.490
Brandon, I saw Donald Trump looking exhausted because of the pressure of the world on his shoulders.

00:14:04.491 --> 00:14:16.546
The Lord is using him for this season to bring forth revival. This is a small window—four years.

00:14:16.547 --> 00:14:24.782
If another plague tries to take place, the window would be even smaller.

00:14:24.783 --> 00:15:02.633
He cannot do this alone. As he steps into office, there will be a mantle on him on the 20th. I saw him cracking that whip, making those devils pop back.

00:15:02.634 --> 00:15:29.077
I saw Kim Jong-un, and the Lord called him the 'Pillsbury Doughboy.'The Lord was very angry and said He was going to humble him in a day.

00:15:29.078 --> 00:16:06.381
He has been in the way too long, and I will humble him like Pharaoh. His days on this earth are numbered.

00:16:06.382 --> 00:16:18.465
Even as he is eliminated, it will take out his sister, for she is just as much of a tyrant.

00:16:18.466 --> 00:16:39.963
There will be a crumbling of the infrastructure and great chaos in North Korea.

00:16:39.964 --> 00:17:07.879
The Iron Curtain that has held back the gospel will be broken, and My gospel will spread throughout North Korea. We've just started the Japan channel today.

00:17:07.880 --> 00:17:35.065
We're going to create channels for all the Asian people in all languages: Philippines, China, Vietnam, and South Korea.

00:17:35.066 --> 00:18:16.381
There will be a great harvest of souls in North Korea. I saw missionaries from South Korea going over the border and snatching people out of the pits of hell.

00:18:16.382 --> 00:18:39.278
The dynasties that have held these people back are going to crumble.

00:18:39.279 --> 00:19:20.059
