00:35:53.302 --> 00:36:07.913
I saw the remnant being blessed. There was light in Goshen and darkness in Egypt.

00:36:07.914 --> 00:36:17.668
There is a dividing line being set up right now, just like the children of Israel on Mount Sinai.

00:36:17.669 --> 00:37:23.916
The ones who ran to the Lord for refuge were safe. There will be a great shaking in the body of Christ from 2025 through 2028 to awaken His church.

00:37:23.917 --> 00:37:44.358
He showed us with catchers'mitts on our hands, in position to catch the harvest because it's coming in fast.

